<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3769305>
    dc:description "FIGURES 4¯6. Plesioschistorchis haridis (Nagaty, 1957) n. comb. (Megaperidae n. comb.: Schistorchiinae) from the common parrotfish, Scarus psittacus Forsskål (Scaridae), from the Red Sea off Egypt. 4. Adult specimen, ventral view. 5. Terminal genitalia, ventral view. 6. Oval eggs. Abbreviations: Ce, Cecum; GP, Genital pore; HD, Hermaphroditic duct; Me, Metraterm; OS, Oral sucker; Ov, Ovary; PC, Prostatic cells; Ph, Pharynx; PP, Pars prostatica; SR, Seminal receptacle; SV, Seminal vesicle; Te, Testes; Ut, Uterus; VD, Vitelline duct; VF, Vitelline follicles; VR, Vitelline reservoir; VS, Ventral sucker." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3769305/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3769315>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15–18. Schistorchis carneus Lühe, 1906 (Megaperidae n. comb.: Schistorchiinae) from the white-spotted puffer, Arothron hispidus (Linnaeus) (Tetraodontidae), from the Red Sea off Egypt. 15. Composite of whole adult specimen, ventral view. 16. Composite of terminal genitalia, ventral view. 17. Composite of proximal female complex, ventral view. 18. Hindbody revealing anterior extent of excretory vesicle and termination of caeca, ventral view. Abbreviations: An, Anus; EA, Excretory arm/duct; Eg, Eggs; EP, Excretory pore; EV, Excretory vesicle; GP, Genital pore; LIC, Left intestinal cecum; Me, Metraterm; MG, Mehlis’ gland; OD, Ovarian duct; Oo, Oötype; OS, Oral sucker; Ov, Ovary; PC, Prostatic cells; Ph, Pharynx; PP, Pars prostatica; RIC, Right intestinal cecum; SR, Seminal receptacle; SV, Seminal vesicle; Te, Testes; Ut, Uterus; VD, Vitelline duct; VF, Vitelline follicles; VR, Vitelline reservoir; VS, Ventral sucker." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3769315/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3769303>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–3. Plesioschistorchis callyodontis (Yamaguti, 1942) n. comb. (Megaperidae n. comb.: Schistorchiinae) from the common parrotfish, Scarus psittacus Forsskål (Scaridae), from the Red Sea off Egypt. 1. Adult specimen, ventral view. 2. Terminal genitalia, ventral view. 3. Elliptical eggs. Abbreviations: Ce, Cecum; EA, Excretory arm/duct; EP, Excretory pore; EV, Excretory vesicle; GP, Genital pore; HD, Hermaphroditic duct; Me, Metraterm; OS, Oral sucker; Ov, Ovary; PC, Prostatic cells; Ph, Pharynx; PM, Parenchymal mass of cells; PP, Pars prostatica; SR, Seminal receptacle; SV, Seminal vesicle; Te, Testes; Ut, Uterus; VF, Vitelline follicles; VS, Ventral sucker." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3769303/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3769307>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7¯8. Paraschistorchis zancli (Hanson, 1953) n. comb. and Paraschistorchis longivesiculurus (Hafeezullah, 1981) n. comb. 7. P. zancli ventral view of adult redrawn from Hanson (1953, Fig. 2a). 8. P. longivesiculurus ventral view of adult redrawn from Hafeezullah (1981, Fig. 1). Abbreviations: An, Anus; Ce, Cecum; EA, Excretory arm/duct; EP, Excretory pore; Es, Esophagus; EV, Excretory vesicle; GP, Genital pore; MG, Mehlis’ gland; OS, Oral sucker; Ov, Ovary; PC, Prostatic cells; Ph, Pharynx; SR, Seminal receptacle; SV, Seminal vesicle; Te, Testes; Ut, Uterus; VD, Vitelline duct; VF, Vitelline follicles; VR, Vitelline reservoir; VS, Ventral sucker." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3769307/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3769309>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9¯10. Paraschistorchis seychellesiensis (Toman, 1989) n. comb. and Paraschistorchis stenosoma (Hanson, 1953) n. comb. 9. P. seychellesiensis ventral view of adult redrawn from Toman (1989, Fig. 2b). 10. P. stenosoma ventral view of adult redrawn from Hanson (1953, Fig. 1a). Abbreviations: An, Anus; Ce, Cecum; EA, Excretory arm/duct; EP, Excretory pore; Es, Esophagus; EV, Excretory vesicle; GP, Genital pore; LC, Laurer’s canal; MG, Mehlis’ gland; OS, Oral sucker; Ov, Ovary; Ph, Pharynx; SR, Seminal receptacle; SV, Seminal vesicle; Te, Testes; Ut, Uterus; VF, Vitelline follicles; VS, Ventral sucker." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3769309/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3769311>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11¯12. Plesioschistorchis callyodontis (Yamaguti, 1942) n. comb. and Plesioschistorchis manteri (Gupta & Tandon, 1984) n. comb. 11. P. callyodontis ventral view of adult redrawn from Yamaguti (1942, Fig. 15). 12. P. manteri ventral view of adult redrawn from Gupta & Tandon (1984, Fig. 1). Abbreviations: Ce, Cecum; EA, Excretory arm/duct; EP, Excretory pore; Es, Esophagus; EV, Excretory vesicle; GP, Genital pore; HD, Hermaphroditic duct; LC, Laurer’s canal; Me, Metraterm; MG, Mehlis’ gland; Oo, Oötype; OS, Oral sucker; Ov, Ovary; PC, Prostatic cells; Ph, Pharynx; PP, Pars prostatica; SR, Seminal receptacle; SV, Seminal vesicle; Te, Testes; Ut, Uterus; VD, Vitelline duct; VF, Vitelline follicles; VR, Vitelline reservoir; VS, Ventral sucker." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3769311/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3769313>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13¯14. Plesioschistorchis sigani (Yamaguti, 1942) n. comb. and Plesioschistorchis haridis (Nagaty, 1957) n. comb. 13. P. sigani ventral view of adult redrawn from Yamaguti (1942, Fig. 16). 14. P. haridis ventral view of adult redrawn from Nagaty (1957, Fig. 1). Abbreviations: Ce, Cecum; EA, Excretory arm/duct; EP, Excretory pore; EV, Excretory vesicle; GP, Genital pore; LC, Laurer’s canal; MG, Mehlis’ gland; OD, Ovarian duct; OS, Oral sucker; Ov, Ovary; Ph, Pharynx; PP, Pars prostatica; SR, Seminal receptacle; SV, Seminal vesicle; Te, Testes; Ut, Uterus; VD, Vitelline duct; VF, Vitelline follicles; VS, Ventral sucker." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3769313/files/figure.png" ;
